"{\"uid\": \"breitbart.com-politics-2024-07-30-ron-desantis-mockery-of-christianity-in-olympic-opening-is-a-symbol-of-cultural-decline\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Florida Gov.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 12, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 7.326722734658041e-12, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ron DeSantis (R) commented on the controversial opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics, noting that the overt mocking of Christianity is a clear \\\"symbol of cultural decline.\\\"\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_DeSantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ron DeSantis\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_DeSantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_DeSantis\"}, {\"begin\": 139, \"end\": 151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9916845465072476, \"rank\": 0.008364486939380668, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"R\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial opening ceremony\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"the overt mocking\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 135}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear \\\"symbol\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 170}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural decline\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The mockery of Christians during the Olympics opening ceremony is a symbol of cultural decline,\\\" DeSantis wrote on social media.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6581302446417983, \"rank\": 0.4433634484660557, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mockery\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"a symbol\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural decline\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"DeSantis\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Elites in Western Europe have rejected the values that made their countries great.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Elites\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"Western Europe\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are fighting that same battle here in the United States-are we going to be rooted in truth?\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that same battle\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the United States\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Florida has made our choice,\\\" he continued, sharing the longer answer he offered during a press conference.\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 7.326722734658041e-12, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our choice\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"the longer answer\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I look at this, this Olympics opening ceremony, and, you know, honestly, like, I wasn't, like, necessarily - I do not get offended,\\\" DeSantis began.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"DeSantis\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People say things that I disagree with all the time, but I was just sad seeing this.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"all the time\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like, you know, that was really a symbol of the decline of Western civilization,\\\" he continued, noting the hypocrisy: I do not think, on the closing ceremony, they are going to do anything where they mock Islam.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a symbol\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the decline\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"Western civilization\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the hypocrisy\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think that's going to happen.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be willing to bet a lot of money that does not happen.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, so, when they are doing tha