ng\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Their segment ended with the three - two males and one female - nearing each other in dramatic kisses, then entering a room to further their amorous acts,\\\" as Breitbart Newsreported.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their segment\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"the three - two males\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"one female\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"dramatic kisses\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"a room\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"their amorous acts\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A drag queen whocarriedthe torch of the Olympic flame in the controversial opening ceremony was pleased about the outrage over the spectacle, which openly mocked Christianity, warning, \\\" We ain't going nowhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2915, \"end\": 2927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9916845465072476, \"rank\": 0.008364486939380668, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A drag queen whocarriedthe torch\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2785}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flame\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"the outrage\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacle\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaselet us knowif you are having issues with commenting.\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Breitbart\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3060